<![CDATA[<font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Hey Grads,</span></font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Thanks for signing up to to volunteer at Ryelands Care Home in Sutton! This email will let you know all the details for the day and what you need to bring.</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">The Project&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Being part of #BlastFromThePast, you will be helping in a local care home and spend the day engaging with residents and taking part in a range of activities which they love to do but are in need of a bit of assistance. This can include teaching them about new technology, helping them write a letter to a relative, or even playing some games. You will also be making a creative mural for a keep sake for the care home in the afternoon, along with putting together some flower poses for the residents to receive.</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">The Celebration&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Being involved in this social action project means you have earned free tickets for the NCS Action Day celebration event taking place in Conway Hall after your project from 4pm to 8pm! You will be travelling from the care home to Conway Hall with your mentor.</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">The details:&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Date: 5th March THIS SATURDAY</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Time: 11am - 3pm&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Location:<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;15 Beddington Gardens, Wallington, Greater London SM6 0JF</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Mentors contact details:&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt;">Phoebe -&nbsp;</span><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre;">	</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">0786 755 3596&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Lee -&nbsp;077856 15037</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Things to bring:&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">- Lunch&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">- Oyster (topped up)</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Tell your friends and we're looking forward to seeing you all there!</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">The Core Grad Team</span></div>]]></td>
